ents and policies related to human de- velopment.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "ea96cf9a-0dcc-4e72-8b4a-f53c1b7b15e9": {"__data__": {"id_": "ea96cf9a-0dcc-4e72-8b4a-f53c1b7b15e9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Potential and Challenges in Human Development: Analysis, Process and Reporting", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "20711853d1140296ffee81cfaf3f612aa03054dc9d16896e51508124d42571e8"}, "2": {"node_id": "16f2fe4e-f226-424f-8d82-443cdae79773", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "22f9d540ae119c6dd7566a7fd5a4f8eb9332b0df6b3b7799c4bed90e8286e0ee"}}, "hash": "0b0cbb8aae80cac88ee1f451200a7af7452622760cc5324d9b9ba5630e1130f6", "text": "In support of the objectives, activities under the regional initiative include: \ufffd Providing support to preparation of regional/ country-cluster human development reports (HDRs) on issues of common concern \ufffd Providing support to producing background tech- nical support documents, policy briefs and appli- cation notes, and impact assessments linked to and complementing sub-regional/regional and na- tional human development reports \ufffd Hosting regional learning seminars on HD \ufffd Facilitating exchange of experiences, best prac- tices and cross-fertilization of ideas and method- ologies through national and regional HD networks \ufffd Assessing and improving advocacy and monitor- ing impact HDRs. I ntroduction The added value of a Regional Programme on Hu- man Development for Asia Pacific is in terms of: \ufffd Compiling experiences from the 57 national hu- man development reports (NHDRs) already pro- duced in the region, and coming up with guide- lines and sharing of best practices \ufffd Contributing to regional cooperation through re- gional research \ufffd Tackling common issues shared by many nations \ufffd Supporting the production of quality reports \ufffd Knowledge sharing through training and exchange of experiences. In line with its mandate and requests from coun- tries in the region, APRI organised its second re- gional training workshop on \u201cPotential and Challenges in Human Development: Analysis, Process and Report- ing\u201d (Phnom Penh, Cambodia, 2-4 May 2004). In", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "cbccc39c-ebd4-4cab-a8ca-38746df13543": {"__data__": {"id_": "cbccc39c-ebd4-4cab-a8ca-38746df13543", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Potential and Challenges in Human Development: Analysis, Process and Reporting", "node_type": null, "metadata"