d Select the HDR theme through: a review of previous HDRs, consultations among national policy makers and other key stakeholders, and brainstorming sessions with partners on theme definition \ufffd Determine the target readership for the HDR through consultation among principal partners \ufffd Through the report drafting process, situation analysis and recommendations within the con- text of the country\u2019s past and existing policy de- velopment plans and policies \ufffd In the event that international consultants are needed, involve the report\u2019s steering committee in selection.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7c20109e-7b4c-46bf-a947-e7159f777ec0": {"__data__": {"id_": "7c20109e-7b4c-46bf-a947-e7159f777ec0", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Potential and Challenges in Human Development: Analysis, Process and Reporting", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "8ad01d86d151a8fb3e01c3c2e82de91672358d2460f91274d08f271010692cf6"}, "2": {"node_id": "b5f78ec9-b781-4377-b238-e5d891bc03a6", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/potential-and-challenges-human-development-analysis-process-and-reporting", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "